skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Rss leader of the Arsenal Football club news.

- Latest 5 news.
- After voice reading, URLs are automatically send to your Alexa.app's home. You can browse each web site by later.
- Update once an hour.

This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by Arsenal Football Club.
Developed by an Arsenal Fan.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
